Hiring re-mapper!

Would you like to make a new version of the map which is up to date, please PM me!

ze_ravenholm_escape_b1:

This is my second escape map, i hope you like it.

As a team you may complete different challenges to make your way to the end. You will have to defend against the zombies and hold the end area for some time. If you manage to complete the mission, the rocket will go off and explode all over. Good luck!

Map specifications:

- Player slots: 64 - FPS: Around 150 - Lightning: Env_sun and environment-lightning

Tips:

The map have 3 secrets included. Be aware of holes you can fall through.

Notification:

If you have any thing to comment on, please let me know.

Credits:

-UA- and Gamebanana

Thanks to everyone who offered feedback and advices on this map. I hope you have fun!
